WEBVTT

00:00.216 --> 00:01.511
<i>Previously on</i> The Originals...

00:01.513 --> 00:04.088
INADU: <i>You will give
me a safe place to hide.</i>

00:04.090 --> 00:07.059
When you die, so too does
your entire sire line.

00:07.061 --> 00:08.659
The great sacrifice,

00:08.661 --> 00:11.564
which will return me to flesh and blood.

00:11.597 --> 00:13.931
FREYA: If Elijah is going
to die one way or another,

00:13.933 --> 00:16.638
then I can try placing his
soul inside the pendant.

00:17.671 --> 00:18.970
Get Elijah into the pendant!

00:18.972 --> 00:20.971
- [yells]
- Hurry, she's killing him!

00:20.973 --> 00:22.573
FREYA: <i>Animam suam.</i>

00:22.575 --> 00:23.642
I can feel him!

00:23.644 --> 00:24.742
[urgent chanting]

00:24.745 --> 00:26.478
<i>She's taken Elijah's power.</i>

00:26.481 --> 00:28.947
<i>The Hollow will be reborn.</i>

00:28.949 --> 00:30.404
My brother's soul is in that pendant.

00:30.406 --> 00:31.825
<i>We need to bring him back.</i>

00:31.828 --> 00:33.852
His original body is where he belongs.

00:33.854 --> 00:35.986
And now that his mind is
stable within the pendant,

00:35.988 --> 00:37.855
I can bring him back, I just...

00:37.857 --> 00:39.657
need a large enough sacrifice.

00:39.660 --> 00:41.283
You're thinking what I'm thinking.

00:41.286 --> 00:42.820
Kill the Hollow, save our brother.

00:44.231 --> 00:46.431
Do me a favor and watch yourself.

00:46.433 --> 00:47.798
What if I told you

00:47.800 --> 00:49.367
<i>I could bring Davina back to life?</i>

00:49.369 --> 00:50.931
- Are you really back?
- Yes.

00:50.934 --> 00:52.636
She and I are now linked.

00:52.638 --> 00:56.374
So, if you want to keep her safe,

00:56.376 --> 00:57.844
then you belong to me.

