01:07.194 --> 01:08.563
Davina?

01:11.491 --> 01:13.627
DAVINA: I'm right here.

01:15.529 --> 01:17.332
[sighs]

01:18.532 --> 01:20.479
Oh, for a moment, I thought...

01:20.482 --> 01:22.000
It's okay.

01:22.002 --> 01:23.167
I'm still me.

01:23.169 --> 01:25.404
Flesh and blood, alive, for now.

01:25.406 --> 01:27.905
And linked to that monster.

01:27.907 --> 01:30.142
I promise, I'm gonna find
a way out of this for you.

01:30.144 --> 01:32.977
She was powerful enough to
bring me back from the dead.

01:32.979 --> 01:35.140
Kol, you have no idea
what we're up against.

01:36.416 --> 01:38.884
Hasn't stopped me before.

01:38.886 --> 01:40.051
Stay here.

01:40.053 --> 01:42.453
I'll be back as soon as I can.

01:42.455 --> 01:44.021
Wait, you're leaving?

01:44.023 --> 01:46.758
Kol, we might not have
much time together.

01:46.760 --> 01:48.996
Losing you broke me.

01:50.531 --> 01:53.664
I will not stand around
and let it happen again.

01:53.666 --> 01:55.901
The Hollow has to be killed.

01:55.903 --> 01:59.036
And if she dies, then I die.

01:59.038 --> 02:01.516
And what's the
alternative, you help her?

02:01.519 --> 02:03.675
You can't betray your family.

02:03.677 --> 02:05.880
That's kind of my specialty.

02:07.648 --> 02:08.916
Stay here.

02:20.661 --> 02:22.096
Are you going somewhere, Kol?

02:24.497 --> 02:26.797
I asked for some time alone with her

02:26.799 --> 02:29.431
before you use me to do your dirty work.

02:29.434 --> 02:33.504
You have been dead 1,500 years,
surely you can spare an hour.

02:33.506 --> 02:36.941
Every second counts if you want
Davina to continue breathing.

02:36.943 --> 02:38.642
What is it that you need, then?

02:38.644 --> 02:40.645
Am I to handle your errands?

02:40.647 --> 02:41.813
Or your laundry?

02:41.815 --> 02:43.614
It's actually quite simple.

02:43.616 --> 02:45.816
I have long wanted to be mortal,

02:45.818 --> 02:48.552
but now that I am alive, I can die.

02:48.554 --> 02:49.754
In fact,

02:49.756 --> 02:53.212
your own family is relentless
in their quest to kill me.

02:53.215 --> 02:55.493
Look, if you want me
to put in a good word,

02:55.495 --> 02:56.994
that ship has sailed, darling.

02:56.996 --> 02:59.129
I have my own protection spell,

02:59.732 --> 03:01.668
cast in the form of a totem.

03:03.237 --> 03:05.570
You will safeguard my totem,

03:05.572 --> 03:07.939
until I'm done with your family.

03:07.941 --> 03:10.774
If you falter,

03:10.776 --> 03:13.143
if any harm comes my way,

03:13.145 --> 03:15.782
Davina will suffer with me.

03:18.711 --> 03:23.580
- <font color="#D81D1D">Synced and corrected by VitoSilans</font> -
-- <font color="#138CE9">www.Addic7ed.com</font> --

03:34.967 --> 03:38.937
The Hollow, she's getting stronger.

03:38.939 --> 03:41.572
You can sense her?

03:41.574 --> 03:44.276
When we first got here, there
was always music outside,

03:44.278 --> 03:47.011
people dancing, laughing.

03:47.013 --> 03:49.947
But since she came back, it's so quiet.

03:49.949 --> 03:52.987
Like she's draining
everything out of the city.

03:57.024 --> 03:59.023
She already took Uncle Elijah.

03:59.025 --> 04:01.659
And soon she will come
for the rest of us.

04:01.661 --> 04:05.296
Listen, Hope, I know you're scared.

04:05.298 --> 04:07.197
But over the years, a lot of bad people

04:07.199 --> 04:09.034
have stood against our family,

04:09.036 --> 04:11.069
and all of them have fallen.

04:11.071 --> 04:14.238
The Hollow is no different.

04:14.240 --> 04:16.543
No, she is different.

04:19.212 --> 04:21.182
♪ ♪

04:36.862 --> 04:38.532
[crackling]

04:41.867 --> 04:43.838
[crackling]

04:51.210 --> 04:52.946
[crackling]

05:00.087 --> 05:02.821
FREYA: Despite the spell I cast,

05:02.823 --> 05:05.956
the very integrity of the
pendant is growing unstable.

05:05.958 --> 05:08.692
It won't be able to hold
Elijah's soul much longer.

05:08.694 --> 05:10.961
We need to find a way
to resurrect him tonight,

05:10.963 --> 05:12.631
or we could lose him forever.

05:12.633 --> 05:15.100
To do that, we'll need more power.

05:15.102 --> 05:16.968
Let me guess, a grand sacrifice.

05:16.970 --> 05:18.464
I say we kill our enemy

05:18.467 --> 05:19.534
and sacrifice her,

05:19.537 --> 05:22.107
then I can channel the power
from the Hollow's death,

05:22.109 --> 05:24.376
raise Elijah's body, and place
him back where he belongs.

05:24.378 --> 05:26.644
- We've tried everything.
- And we've come close.

05:26.646 --> 05:29.114
Labonair blood is her Achilles' heel.

05:29.116 --> 05:30.715
Hayley, your blood

05:30.717 --> 05:33.117
weakened her, but you've
technically been dead for years.

05:33.119 --> 05:35.787
So it won't be strong
enough to kill her.

05:35.789 --> 05:37.655
If we forge a blade using the blood

05:37.657 --> 05:39.391
of the last living Labonair...

05:39.393 --> 05:41.158
We don't want Hope involved.

05:41.160 --> 05:42.961
FREYA: She's already involved.

05:42.963 --> 05:45.864
Hope has been obsessed with the
symbol that follows the Hollow:

05:45.866 --> 05:47.297
the serpent consuming itself.

05:47.299 --> 05:49.768
Now, I believe this
is showing us the key,

05:49.770 --> 05:51.769
the only means to which
she can be destroyed,

05:51.771 --> 05:52.772
her own blood.

05:56.003 --> 05:59.143
The Hollow's one end of
the Labonair bloodline.

05:59.145 --> 06:01.812
Hope is the other. And we
need to close that loop.

06:01.814 --> 06:04.348
The best way to do that is
for Hayley to wield a weapon

06:04.350 --> 06:05.783
forged with Hope's blood.

06:05.785 --> 06:08.221
When she stabs her, it's only then

06:08.224 --> 06:11.344
the Hollow can be
obliterated completely.

06:13.460 --> 06:16.547
Then we make it work. I'll talk to Hope.

06:22.335 --> 06:24.732
Well, hey there.

06:24.735 --> 06:26.737
Uh, it's me again.

06:26.739 --> 06:29.041
Hope, uh, all is well where you are.

06:29.044 --> 06:31.042
You know, I really
would love to talk to you

06:31.044 --> 06:36.047
about a few... hundred things.

06:36.049 --> 06:38.482
Like how Eddie uses this

06:38.484 --> 06:42.052
weird baby voice anytime he
says "hi" to a random dog.

06:42.054 --> 06:43.987
I don't know, might be a deal breaker.

06:43.989 --> 06:45.464
[chuckles]

06:45.467 --> 06:48.492
Or how I finally watched <i>Practical Magic.</i>

06:48.494 --> 06:50.728
And you were right.

06:50.730 --> 06:51.898
Perfect movie.

06:53.934 --> 06:56.134
Or, you know...

06:56.136 --> 06:58.071
how freakin' much I still miss you.

07:00.340 --> 07:03.340
I miss her, too.

07:03.342 --> 07:04.679
Hey.

07:07.047 --> 07:08.747
Next time, we should carpool.

07:08.749 --> 07:11.516
Actually, I'm looking for Vincent.

07:11.518 --> 07:14.985
He said he'd find a cure for
Sofya, but he's been M.I.A.

07:14.987 --> 07:16.156
Have you seen him?

07:17.390 --> 07:18.793
No.

07:20.761 --> 07:23.261
What, you want some help finding him?

07:23.263 --> 07:24.896
No.

07:24.898 --> 07:27.268
No, but if you see him,
why don't you call me.

07:30.925 --> 07:33.261
FREYA: <i>Dauha naer do smrti.</i>

07:34.508 --> 07:36.374
<i>Dauha naer do smrti.</i>

07:36.376 --> 07:38.212
<i>Dauha naer do smrti.</i>

07:40.446 --> 07:42.814
That's a rather odd locator spell.

07:42.816 --> 07:44.915
I'm trying to trace the Hollow's magic.

07:44.917 --> 07:46.785
Almost have it.

07:46.787 --> 07:48.519
[sizzling]

07:48.521 --> 07:51.124
She's in the Garden District.

07:52.191 --> 07:54.091
That's the LaForge House.

07:54.093 --> 07:56.798
At one time, it was the
center of high society,

07:56.801 --> 07:58.028
but that all changed when

07:58.030 --> 08:00.531
Dr. LaForge tortured and
killed his friends and family.

08:00.533 --> 08:03.934
Claimed until his dying day that
an evil spirit made him do it.

08:03.936 --> 08:07.273
That house has been derelict since.

08:09.075 --> 08:12.811
The perfect lair for
someone who relishes tragedy.

08:15.609 --> 08:17.077
[sizzling continues]

08:17.883 --> 08:19.283
REBEKAH: What's that?

08:19.285 --> 08:21.182
If the serpent

08:21.185 --> 08:24.288
at the LaForge House
represents the Hollow herself,

08:24.290 --> 08:26.557
then this must be some sort of totem

08:26.559 --> 08:29.561
she's using to magnify her
power and protect herself.

08:29.563 --> 08:31.295
Dahlia used to use these

08:31.297 --> 08:34.565
when she was up to
something particularly awful.

08:34.567 --> 08:37.234
It will render the Hollow unkillable.

08:37.236 --> 08:40.337
We will have to destroy
it before we can face her.

08:40.340 --> 08:42.006
Lovely.

08:42.008 --> 08:43.607
I could do with some fresh air.

08:43.609 --> 08:44.979
And some fresh blood.

08:46.446 --> 08:48.445
Take the map.

08:48.447 --> 08:50.515
It's been spelled to track the totem.

08:50.517 --> 08:52.286
Don't go alone.

08:53.320 --> 08:55.152
One step ahead of you, sis.

08:55.154 --> 08:56.320
KOL: Hey, Bex.

08:56.322 --> 08:58.088
What's up?

08:58.090 --> 08:59.692
Someone's floating around

08:59.695 --> 09:01.593
with a trinket that's
fueling our enemy's power.

09:01.595 --> 09:04.999
What say you help me track down
and exterminate this scoundrel?

09:06.199 --> 09:08.131
I'd like nothing better.

09:08.133 --> 09:10.104
Perfect.

09:25.806 --> 09:27.775
[birds chirping]

09:31.612 --> 09:33.647
♪ ♪

09:37.005 --> 09:40.217
You're not seriously going
in there alone, are you?

09:40.219 --> 09:41.486
Why not?

09:41.488 --> 09:44.622
As far as threats go, the only
person with the means to kill me

09:44.624 --> 09:46.114
is lurking right out here.

09:46.117 --> 09:48.559
I'm not a threat to you, the
Hollow, on the other hand, is.

09:48.561 --> 09:51.196
The Hollow's got some
acolyte protecting a totem

09:51.198 --> 09:52.363
that magnifies her power,

09:52.365 --> 09:54.533
making her unkillable.

09:54.535 --> 09:56.668
Trouble is, we have to end this tonight.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.812
Hayley's got the means.

09:57.815 --> 09:59.507
I just need to make
sure she's vulnerable.

10:01.307 --> 10:03.875
Kol's coming to watch my back,
so you can just scamper off.

10:03.877 --> 10:06.178
What kind of gentlemen would I be

10:06.180 --> 10:07.714
if I didn't offer to escort you?

10:18.525 --> 10:20.958
You're the king of this city.
Can't you condemn this dump?

10:20.960 --> 10:22.593
How about we skip the criticism

10:22.595 --> 10:24.395
and just focus on
what we're looking for?

10:24.397 --> 10:26.178
KOL: Totem's not here.

10:26.181 --> 10:29.123
I scoured the house.
There's no sign of it.

10:29.126 --> 10:30.501
You were supposed to wait for me.

10:30.503 --> 10:31.303
Well, I got bored.

10:31.305 --> 10:32.670
And it looks like you got accosted

10:32.672 --> 10:34.056
by the local riffraff.

10:34.059 --> 10:35.273
Oh, you got a problem?

10:35.275 --> 10:37.876
Get over yourselves. All right?

10:37.878 --> 10:40.043
The map says that the
totem is still here,

10:40.046 --> 10:42.347
so it must be hidden
somewhere in this hovel.

10:42.349 --> 10:44.448
Look, if you don't trust me,

10:44.450 --> 10:46.454
help yourself. Come on in.

10:47.554 --> 10:48.953
[barrier hums]

10:48.955 --> 10:50.157
What...

10:54.293 --> 10:55.860
What the hell, Kol?

10:55.862 --> 10:57.795
A dark object? Really?

10:57.797 --> 10:59.698
Kol, you better undo this right now.

10:59.700 --> 11:02.833
I'm sorry, Rebekah.

11:02.835 --> 11:04.369
I truly am.

11:04.371 --> 11:06.474
Why are you helping her?

11:07.832 --> 11:09.062
What has she done to you?

11:26.627 --> 11:28.329
I don't want to.

11:29.863 --> 11:32.429
Are you scared it's gonna hurt?

11:32.431 --> 11:35.567
I'm scared if I do this,
you're gonna pick a fight.

11:35.569 --> 11:38.903
And the Hollow, she can hurt you.

11:38.905 --> 11:42.874
I know you're scared.

11:42.876 --> 11:45.943
I wish we didn't have to
have this conversation.

11:45.945 --> 11:48.746
When I was your age, I had
to deal with a lot of things

11:48.748 --> 11:50.881
that I didn't want to deal with either.

11:50.883 --> 11:54.419
I didn't want that for
you, but here we are.

11:54.421 --> 11:56.131
The thing is,

11:56.134 --> 11:58.756
sometimes you have to do
things that you don't want to do

11:58.758 --> 12:01.326
because you're the only
one that can do them.

12:01.328 --> 12:03.361
Like you.

12:03.363 --> 12:04.962
Like me.

12:04.964 --> 12:06.901
Okay.

12:10.070 --> 12:11.472
[sighs softly]

12:21.448 --> 12:22.947
Rebekah's not answering.

12:22.949 --> 12:24.381
Neither is Kol.

12:24.383 --> 12:25.801
The sooner we end this the better.

12:25.804 --> 12:28.985
No. We have to assume that
Inadu's totem is still intact.

12:28.988 --> 12:31.389
We cannot attack her
until we destroy it.

12:31.391 --> 12:33.457
Go after Rebekah,

12:33.459 --> 12:34.491
find the totem.

12:34.494 --> 12:35.860
I'm not leaving Hayley alone.

12:35.862 --> 12:37.090
We're out of time.

12:37.093 --> 12:39.060
The cracks are getting worse.

12:39.900 --> 12:41.332
I need you

12:41.334 --> 12:42.634
to destroy the totem.

12:42.636 --> 12:43.967
I'll go with Hayley.

12:43.969 --> 12:45.804
And what about Hope?

12:45.806 --> 12:47.405
Compel her a nanny.

12:47.407 --> 12:49.073
We don't have another choice.

12:49.075 --> 12:52.544
You're the best advantage we got.

12:52.546 --> 12:55.744
Be fast, be brutal, destroy the totem,

12:55.747 --> 12:57.351
or we're dead.

13:02.689 --> 13:04.759
Here. For you and Hayley tonight.

13:06.426 --> 13:08.892
Anoint these with a
drop of Hope's blood.

13:08.894 --> 13:10.664
They'll serve you well.

13:13.966 --> 13:15.710
You should destroy this.

13:15.713 --> 13:17.602
Hayley could die.

13:17.604 --> 13:19.837
And why is her life more
important than yours?

13:19.839 --> 13:22.723
I can't take a little girl's
mother away from her, Kol.

13:22.726 --> 13:24.099
All right, then we just
have to find another way

13:24.101 --> 13:25.443
to get you out of this.

13:25.445 --> 13:27.611
Because there is no
way I'm letting you go.

13:27.613 --> 13:29.581
I've been thinking,

13:29.583 --> 13:31.882
Elijah once gave me one
of your mother's spells.

13:31.884 --> 13:33.784
It used to break a magical link.

13:33.786 --> 13:35.087
I'm too weak right now,

13:35.089 --> 13:37.650
but if we could find a coven to
counter Inadu's spell, then...

13:37.653 --> 13:40.058
No, I know the spell.
And we don't need a coven,

13:40.060 --> 13:42.595
we just need one powerful little witch.

13:48.634 --> 13:50.735
[keys jingle]

13:50.737 --> 13:54.539
I have a car in the lot out back.

13:54.541 --> 13:58.041
If I'm not back by midnight,
you take it and you go.

13:58.043 --> 14:00.879
Wait, without you? What...

14:00.881 --> 14:03.113
Are you kidding? What are you doing?

14:03.115 --> 14:04.649
Davina, I'm not asking.

14:04.651 --> 14:06.387
I need you to do this.

14:08.488 --> 14:09.721
Promise me.

14:09.723 --> 14:11.758
Yeah.

14:26.672 --> 14:28.354
I sealed these with Hope's blood.

14:28.357 --> 14:29.620
One for each of us.

14:29.623 --> 14:33.295
Once the totem is destroyed,
we can sacrifice the Hollow.

14:35.916 --> 14:38.116
Are you okay?

14:38.118 --> 14:40.083
Yeah.

14:40.085 --> 14:41.653
[chuckles softly]

14:41.655 --> 14:43.688
I never thought twice
about fighting or dying

14:43.690 --> 14:45.589
for family before.

14:45.591 --> 14:46.924
But now, with Keelin...

14:46.926 --> 14:48.492
Now you have someone you're afraid

14:48.494 --> 14:50.029
you're not gonna make it home to.

14:51.797 --> 14:54.466
You will make it home, Freya.

14:54.468 --> 14:55.935
I got your back.

14:58.171 --> 15:00.071
Hayley.

15:00.073 --> 15:02.674
I know we haven't
always seen eye-to-eye,

15:02.676 --> 15:06.881
but... well, I suppose
family rarely does.

15:18.691 --> 15:20.661
[door creaks]

15:29.002 --> 15:30.968
[door slams]

15:30.970 --> 15:33.139
I guess she knows we're here.

15:43.983 --> 15:45.753
♪ ♪

15:56.695 --> 15:59.666
[door creaks]

16:07.706 --> 16:08.708
[neck snaps]

16:13.179 --> 16:14.482
[groans softly]

16:21.021 --> 16:22.522
[grunts]

16:26.126 --> 16:29.177
There you are.

16:29.180 --> 16:30.180
Jackson?

16:30.183 --> 16:32.099
Been waiting for you.

16:48.033 --> 16:51.033
How am I here? How are you here?

16:51.035 --> 16:53.001
I'm no expert, but I'm
guessing you're going through

16:53.003 --> 16:55.004
some kind of psychological
break right now.

16:55.006 --> 16:56.972
You've been through hell.

16:56.974 --> 17:02.144
So your mind took you
somewhere peaceful,

17:02.146 --> 17:04.146
Honestly, I'm flattered
you thought of me.

17:04.147 --> 17:07.784
Figured your happy place
would be somewhere with Elijah.

17:07.786 --> 17:09.318
So...

17:09.319 --> 17:11.809
if I'm unconscious,
then I need to wake up.

17:11.811 --> 17:13.676
I know.

17:13.680 --> 17:16.092
I know. I'm on your side.
We'll get you back in the fight,

17:16.094 --> 17:18.746
before the Hollow finishes
whatever she started.

17:27.637 --> 17:29.204
Hey, buddy.

17:29.206 --> 17:31.708
Are my mom and dad back?

17:31.710 --> 17:35.131
Not quite.

17:35.134 --> 17:39.314
Hey, you know what I used to
do, when I was bored at your age?

17:39.317 --> 17:40.782
Magic.

17:40.784 --> 17:43.685
I'm not supposed to do
magic with strangers.

17:43.687 --> 17:45.585
What?

17:45.588 --> 17:47.022
I-I'm family.

17:47.024 --> 17:48.960
So why did you go away?

17:53.130 --> 17:56.833
I went away because I was sad.

17:56.835 --> 18:00.002
And I thought I'd never be happy again.

18:00.004 --> 18:01.804
And I didn't want to make everybody

18:01.806 --> 18:04.109
that I loved around me sad, too.

18:27.331 --> 18:29.267
[gasping softly]

18:50.855 --> 18:52.790
Hayley?

18:53.924 --> 18:56.692
FREYA: Hayley?

18:56.694 --> 18:58.797
Hayley?

19:00.030 --> 19:03.365
No. More wolfsbane.

19:03.367 --> 19:06.105
I want her alive, but barely.

19:07.517 --> 19:09.853
She still has a part to play.

19:36.401 --> 19:37.903
No. No, no, no.

19:39.568 --> 19:41.205
You were supposed to be...

19:43.907 --> 19:45.974
This isn't real.

19:45.976 --> 19:47.679
No, you can't be dead.

19:48.812 --> 19:50.779
You aren't dead.

19:50.781 --> 19:51.684
Not yet.

19:52.574 --> 19:53.950
But I will be.

19:53.952 --> 19:56.384
[sniffles]

19:56.386 --> 19:59.955
No cell service to call
your precious Sonya.

19:59.957 --> 20:02.290
Sofya.

20:02.292 --> 20:04.126
Apologies.

20:04.128 --> 20:07.095
I can't be expected to remember
the names of wanton trollops.

20:07.097 --> 20:10.266
Listen, I'm gonna ask you nicely
to shut the hell up about her.

20:10.268 --> 20:12.501
You know what?

20:12.503 --> 20:14.871
Why don't we just burn the house down?

20:14.873 --> 20:17.339
Oh, don't be so dramatic.

20:17.341 --> 20:18.841
Dramatic?

20:18.843 --> 20:21.376
I'm not running late
for a manicure, Marcel.

20:21.378 --> 20:23.787
Time is running out to resurrect Elijah,

20:23.790 --> 20:25.314
Hayley's on a suicide mission,

20:25.316 --> 20:27.415
and I can't lose anyone else I love.

20:27.417 --> 20:30.636
I have reached my quota
of heartbreak for the year.

20:30.639 --> 20:31.673
Rebekah...

20:31.676 --> 20:34.156
How ironic.

20:34.158 --> 20:36.526
Two of the world's most powerful beings

20:36.528 --> 20:40.061
trapped in a magical butterfly net.

20:40.063 --> 20:42.431
Tell me you weren't overwhelmed
by some brain-dead witch.

20:42.433 --> 20:44.232
No, our biggest mistake was trusting Kol

20:44.234 --> 20:46.480
- for one second of his life.
- What?

20:46.483 --> 20:48.805
Kol is protecting the
totem for the Hollow.

20:48.807 --> 20:51.507
Who knows why, or what she offered him.

20:51.509 --> 20:53.878
I don't care what she
offered him. Where is he?

20:59.049 --> 21:00.816
He's at the compound.

21:00.819 --> 21:02.856
Go.

21:06.089 --> 21:07.890
I need to snap out of this.

21:07.892 --> 21:10.529
If I don't, we could
lose Elijah forever.

21:13.530 --> 21:15.166
Is he good to you?

21:18.203 --> 21:20.169
Hey, talk to me.

21:20.171 --> 21:22.407
It ain't gonna kill me.

21:25.242 --> 21:27.512
He has been good to me.

21:28.579 --> 21:30.546
But when I fell for him,

21:30.548 --> 21:33.249
I was scared of Klaus, of...

21:33.251 --> 21:37.586
being a mom, and he made me feel safe.

21:37.588 --> 21:40.556
But now, I...

21:40.558 --> 21:43.459
Well, if you wanted safety,
you would've loved me.

21:43.461 --> 21:45.327
I chose you. I married you.

21:45.329 --> 21:47.465
But you were in love with him.

21:49.067 --> 21:50.566
[scoffs]

21:50.568 --> 21:54.036
I mean, it's an old, sad story.

21:54.038 --> 21:57.606
The monsters treated you like crap,

21:57.608 --> 22:00.142
turned you into a girl
who loves monsters.

22:00.144 --> 22:03.214
You're not helping
me. You're stalling me.

22:04.949 --> 22:06.082
[grunts]

22:06.084 --> 22:08.617
[laughs]

22:08.619 --> 22:09.885
No.

22:09.887 --> 22:11.086
[laughs]

22:11.088 --> 22:12.323
Oh, you're not you.

22:13.324 --> 22:14.990
You're the Hollow.

22:14.992 --> 22:16.294
[grunts]

22:29.374 --> 22:31.343
[grunting]

22:44.454 --> 22:45.590
[groans]

22:56.934 --> 22:58.870
[magic hums]

23:13.684 --> 23:15.186
You're wasting your energy.

23:21.024 --> 23:22.601
You're a vision.

23:22.604 --> 23:23.929
You can't hurt me.

23:23.932 --> 23:25.549
[chuckles]

23:25.552 --> 23:27.488
You still don't get it, do you?

23:31.703 --> 23:33.702
The Hollow is more powerful

23:33.704 --> 23:36.308
than you can possibly imagine.

23:37.474 --> 23:39.040
[grunts]

23:39.042 --> 23:42.026
[groans, gasps]

23:55.699 --> 23:57.364
Suppose your girlfriend won't be happy

23:57.366 --> 23:59.433
that you spent the entire day with me.

23:59.435 --> 24:02.438
Sofya hasn't woken since
the Hollow invaded her mind.

24:03.772 --> 24:05.974
You could at least feign sympathy.

24:05.976 --> 24:08.776
Why? She shot me.

24:08.778 --> 24:10.153
Multiple times.

24:10.156 --> 24:12.546
Is that really the reason
why you hate her so much?

24:12.548 --> 24:14.184
[chuckles]

24:15.551 --> 24:17.584
Okay.

24:17.586 --> 24:19.222
[lighter clicking]

24:29.999 --> 24:31.666
What the hell are you doing?

24:31.668 --> 24:33.470
The main gas line's got to be down here.

24:35.071 --> 24:37.572
At least it'll help
torch the place faster,

24:37.574 --> 24:39.439
unless you prefer a slow burn.

24:39.441 --> 24:40.883
Thought you wanted to wait it out.

24:42.812 --> 24:44.012
[gas hissing]

24:44.014 --> 24:45.084
Do you?

24:57.727 --> 25:01.487
If I untie this knot...

25:01.490 --> 25:04.064
your girlfriend will
be free from the Hollow?

25:04.066 --> 25:05.699
I hope so.

25:05.701 --> 25:08.736
And you really love her?

25:08.738 --> 25:10.602
Yes.

25:10.605 --> 25:12.505
Kind of like your mom loves, uh...

25:12.508 --> 25:14.042
Uncle Elijah.

25:14.044 --> 25:17.055
You are miraculously well-adjusted.

25:26.056 --> 25:28.558
[grunts]

25:29.625 --> 25:31.426
[panting]

25:31.428 --> 25:33.960
Why are you doing this?

25:33.962 --> 25:36.096
[grunts]

25:36.098 --> 25:38.399
All I ever wanted was to protect you!

25:38.401 --> 25:42.035
[laughs]: And now you're gonna die here.

25:42.037 --> 25:43.406
- No.
- [grunts]

25:45.808 --> 25:47.443
Hayley!

25:49.511 --> 25:51.447
[grunting, shouting]

25:55.951 --> 25:57.685
If you were stronger,

25:57.687 --> 25:59.887
then...

25:59.889 --> 26:02.489
You're not here.

26:02.491 --> 26:04.124
[chuckles] I'm always here.

26:04.126 --> 26:07.527
This is the vision of me
that keeps you up at night,

26:07.529 --> 26:09.899
the fear of what you
know to be inevitable.

26:16.940 --> 26:18.542
[grunting]

26:30.753 --> 26:34.654
All right. Focus on the knot, luv.

26:34.656 --> 26:37.160
It's very important,
and I'll be right back.

26:43.566 --> 26:45.999
I imagine right now you're
rather cross with me.

26:46.001 --> 26:48.468
You should know I have my reasons.

26:48.470 --> 26:50.004
Rebekah suggested I hear them.

26:50.006 --> 26:52.776
I'd rather rip out your vocal chords.

26:54.798 --> 26:56.412
[groans]

27:05.488 --> 27:07.458
♪ ♪

27:12.528 --> 27:14.631
Hey, sorry, we're closed.

27:19.568 --> 27:21.838
Well, maybe you can make an exception.

27:29.112 --> 27:31.144
Davina?

27:31.146 --> 27:33.547
I don't know how long I have,

27:33.549 --> 27:36.851
but I had to see you to thank you.

27:36.853 --> 27:40.153
Wh-What do you mean?
Thank me? For what?

27:40.155 --> 27:42.523
For visiting me.

27:42.525 --> 27:45.526
And for talking to me.

27:45.528 --> 27:46.864
You heard it?

27:47.931 --> 27:50.797
Y-You were there.

27:50.799 --> 27:52.970
Josh, I was always there.

27:55.971 --> 27:57.673
[chuckles]

28:02.612 --> 28:05.212
Now stop and listen. I
did what I did for Davina.

28:05.214 --> 28:07.450
The Hollow brought her
back, and now they're linked.

28:07.453 --> 28:09.552
I just need a bloody
second to set her free.

28:10.586 --> 28:11.718
[grunts]

28:11.720 --> 28:13.054
Lovesick imbecile.

28:13.056 --> 28:15.222
The Hollow preys upon your weakness.

28:15.224 --> 28:18.191
She raised Davina to get you
to betray your family, and you,

28:18.193 --> 28:20.747
pathetic as you are,
leapt at the chance.

28:23.185 --> 28:25.185
Our family owes Davina that much.

28:25.187 --> 28:28.056
I owe nothing to her.

28:28.058 --> 28:29.958
Nor to you.

28:29.960 --> 28:32.426
JACKSON: You saw it:

28:32.428 --> 28:34.962
the violence,

28:34.964 --> 28:36.830
the rage.

28:36.832 --> 28:38.500
[groans]

28:38.502 --> 28:40.835
That's what he is.

28:40.837 --> 28:44.505
You fell for the suit, Hayley.

28:44.507 --> 28:46.907
You were blinded

28:46.909 --> 28:48.912
by his charade.

28:49.980 --> 28:50.945
You're not Jackson,

28:50.947 --> 28:52.981
and you don't deserve to wear his face.

28:52.983 --> 28:54.385
[grunting]

29:03.309 --> 29:05.026
- [grunts]
- [shouts]

29:05.028 --> 29:07.561
You're right.

29:07.563 --> 29:09.734
Jackson was good.

29:11.301 --> 29:13.270
[groans, wheezes]

29:15.405 --> 29:16.474
And me...

29:20.409 --> 29:21.576
[panting]

29:21.578 --> 29:23.010
[chokes]

29:23.012 --> 29:24.546
well, I was never good.

29:24.548 --> 29:25.914
[groans]

29:25.916 --> 29:27.283
No, Nik, please.

29:34.558 --> 29:36.156
Hayley.

29:36.158 --> 29:37.392
Hey.

29:37.394 --> 29:39.359
Are you all right?

29:39.361 --> 29:40.763
Did Klaus break the totem?

29:40.766 --> 29:42.065
I hope so.

29:42.068 --> 29:43.763
But we can't wait.

29:43.766 --> 29:45.665
You need to stab the Hollow.

29:45.668 --> 29:47.778
You think you'll be strong enough?

29:51.441 --> 29:52.910
Let's do this.

29:55.044 --> 29:57.045
No, Nik.

29:57.047 --> 29:58.737
I need a little time.

29:58.740 --> 30:00.548
I just need to know she's alive.

30:00.550 --> 30:03.084
Please, grant me this small mercy.

30:03.086 --> 30:06.186
Mercy is a privilege
reserved for family.

30:06.188 --> 30:08.923
Your status has been revoked.

30:08.925 --> 30:10.591
Brother, no! Please!

30:10.593 --> 30:13.797
For a thousand years, I've
never experienced love or peace.

30:14.630 --> 30:17.065
Davina changed me. [grunts]

30:17.067 --> 30:18.899
What if it was Camille?

30:18.901 --> 30:20.601
What if it could bring her back?!

30:20.603 --> 30:22.305
Would you not do as I did?!

30:23.639 --> 30:25.475
[grunting]

30:41.957 --> 30:43.560
INADU: <i>Cencahua ezhuia.</i>

30:44.593 --> 30:46.496
<i>Cencahua ezhuia.</i>

30:47.496 --> 30:49.499
<i>Cencahua ezhuia.</i>

30:50.599 --> 30:53.102
<i>Cencahua ezhuia.</i>

30:58.241 --> 31:00.477
<i>Cuauhtzicoa calpanpilli.</i>

31:01.393 --> 31:03.296
<i>Cuauhtzicoa calpanpilli.</i>

31:14.189 --> 31:15.325
[door opens]

31:17.526 --> 31:19.062
[shouts]

31:24.606 --> 31:26.067
First,

31:26.069 --> 31:28.135
- I will break your body.
- [groans]

31:28.137 --> 31:31.138
Then I will break your spirit.

31:31.140 --> 31:33.708
Your spirit is nearly
broken already, isn't it?

31:33.710 --> 31:35.145
[groans]

31:39.314 --> 31:41.014
Hey, what's wrong?

31:41.016 --> 31:42.986
[groaning]

31:48.908 --> 31:50.677
Do it.

31:55.111 --> 31:57.247
No. No!

32:01.737 --> 32:03.206
[shouting]

32:05.746 --> 32:07.474
That's enough! That's enough!

32:07.476 --> 32:10.013
She's gone.

32:13.282 --> 32:14.581
She's gone.

32:14.583 --> 32:16.286
[both panting]

32:28.470 --> 32:30.439
♪ ♪

32:46.587 --> 32:48.857
[siren wailing, emergency horn honking]

32:51.926 --> 32:53.893
Are you all right?

32:53.895 --> 32:56.363
You know how I love to blow things up.

32:56.365 --> 32:57.695
Good night.

32:58.866 --> 33:00.866
We were in love for two centuries,

33:00.868 --> 33:03.101
and now we're setting
fires to avoid each other.

33:03.104 --> 33:04.304
All right, what the hell happened?

33:04.306 --> 33:05.739
I woke up from a dagger nap

33:05.741 --> 33:07.473
to find you trying to
kill everyone that I love.

33:07.475 --> 33:08.925
Your brother ripped my heart out

33:08.928 --> 33:10.743
and then tossed my body off a bridge.

33:10.745 --> 33:12.222
And I didn't even see you crying.

33:12.225 --> 33:13.613
I mourned the man I thought I knew.

33:13.615 --> 33:15.448
Well, I'm sorry, I must have missed that

33:15.450 --> 33:16.783
while you were trying to curse me.

33:16.785 --> 33:18.317
I asked you to leave with me!

33:18.319 --> 33:21.887
Seven years ago, I asked you.

33:21.889 --> 33:24.891
But you didn't love me as
much as you love New Orleans.

33:24.893 --> 33:27.427
All right, I do love New
Orleans, all right, I do.

33:27.429 --> 33:29.629
And I watched it burn
to the ground for you

33:29.631 --> 33:30.997
once before, Rebekah.

33:30.999 --> 33:32.902
And then I waited a century...

33:34.204 --> 33:35.768
and you didn't even come back for me.

33:35.770 --> 33:37.740
So you just forgot about me?

33:39.840 --> 33:43.008
You know, it's probably best
if you just do that again.

33:43.010 --> 33:45.912
Yeah, you know what, I think
it's best for both of us.

33:45.914 --> 33:47.805
Couldn't agree more.

33:47.808 --> 33:49.010
Yeah.

33:56.325 --> 33:57.827
♪ ♪

34:07.502 --> 34:09.404
[whispers]: Damn it.

34:15.710 --> 34:18.812
♪ You're a bow and arrow ♪

34:18.813 --> 34:20.946
♪ A broken guitar ♪

34:20.947 --> 34:26.553
♪ While the rainwater
washes away who you are ♪

34:26.554 --> 34:29.195
♪ We go over the mountains... ♪

34:29.197 --> 34:30.556
If Klaus got to him...

34:30.558 --> 34:32.859
Then you have to leave anyway.

34:32.860 --> 34:34.578
♪ Over the mountains... ♪

34:34.581 --> 34:36.962
Davina, you almost died back there.

34:36.964 --> 34:40.567
♪ You're a bow and arrow... ♪

34:40.569 --> 34:42.569
Look, you remember the first day we met?

34:42.571 --> 34:45.071
You told me you wanted to be normal.

34:45.072 --> 34:47.107
You said "normal's relative."

34:47.109 --> 34:51.511
Yeah, well, you're a
twice-resurrected Harvest Girl

34:51.513 --> 34:53.645
with an Original vampire boyfriend.

34:53.647 --> 34:55.547
Normal's always gonna be relative.

34:55.549 --> 34:59.664
But with or without him,
you have to take this chance.

34:59.667 --> 35:00.655
You deserve it.

35:02.390 --> 35:04.556
I can't just leave him.

35:04.558 --> 35:06.219
KOL: Well, that sounds

35:06.222 --> 35:08.455
like a broken promise.

35:08.458 --> 35:13.098
♪ And I want you to close my eyes... ♪

35:13.100 --> 35:15.134
I thought that you
were daggered, or worse.

35:15.136 --> 35:17.736
I caught Klaus in a
rare charitable moment.

35:17.738 --> 35:19.374
But it won't last long.

35:20.674 --> 35:22.475
Are you ready to go?

35:22.477 --> 35:24.910
Anywhere.

35:24.912 --> 35:26.014
Anywhere?

35:27.082 --> 35:28.750
Everywhere.

35:36.857 --> 35:40.493
♪ I want you to hold my hands... ♪

35:40.495 --> 35:42.094
Thank you.

35:42.097 --> 35:46.031
♪ Over my heart... ♪

35:46.033 --> 35:47.634
I love you.

35:47.636 --> 35:49.636
♪ I want you to close my eyes... ♪

35:49.638 --> 35:50.873
I love you, too.

35:53.607 --> 35:58.044
♪ When it grows dark... ♪

35:58.046 --> 36:00.980
Now get out of here. Go.

36:02.797 --> 36:05.598
♪ A broken guitar ♪

36:05.601 --> 36:10.938
♪ While the rainwater
washes away who you are ♪

36:10.941 --> 36:14.609
♪ We go over the mountains ♪

36:14.612 --> 36:16.767
♪ And under the stars ♪

36:16.770 --> 36:19.616
♪ We go over the mountains ♪

36:19.619 --> 36:22.656
♪ And under the stars. ♪

36:49.097 --> 36:51.864
Hayley asked me to give you the knife.

36:51.866 --> 36:54.500
She's not going to be
here for when Elijah wakes?

36:54.502 --> 36:58.638
She said there was
something she had to do.

36:58.640 --> 37:03.109
Oh, well, you know as well as anyone

37:03.111 --> 37:06.111
how the Hollow meddles in your mind,

37:06.113 --> 37:10.683
clawing at your oldest
wounds, making them new again.

37:10.685 --> 37:13.789
Well, at least you have
someone to comfort you now.

37:15.156 --> 37:17.723
Where is Keelin?

37:17.725 --> 37:20.792
I told her that we needed
some family time tonight.

37:20.794 --> 37:23.162
We'll see her tomorrow.

37:23.164 --> 37:25.133
♪ ♪

37:29.671 --> 37:32.971
Freya, are you all right?

37:32.973 --> 37:35.140
Yeah.

37:35.142 --> 37:36.808
I just need to focus.

37:36.810 --> 37:41.147
The Hollow killed our
brother for her own ends.

37:41.149 --> 37:43.883
It's only fitting that we
use hers to bring him home.

37:43.885 --> 37:46.752
Give me your hands.

37:46.754 --> 37:48.654
[breathes deeply]

37:48.656 --> 37:51.256
[exhales]

37:51.258 --> 37:55.261
<i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

37:55.263 --> 37:57.163
<i>Verha hel igjen.</i>

37:57.165 --> 38:01.033
<i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

38:01.035 --> 38:05.605
<i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

38:05.607 --> 38:09.299
♪ Lover, hunter, friend and enemy ♪

38:09.302 --> 38:13.178
♪ You will always be
every one of these ♪

38:13.180 --> 38:17.951
♪ Lover, hunter, friend and enemy ♪

38:17.953 --> 38:21.087
♪ You will always be
every one of these ♪

38:21.089 --> 38:26.662
♪ Nothing's fair in love and war ♪

38:37.104 --> 38:39.138
♪ In life... ♪

38:39.140 --> 38:41.042
Jack...

38:43.078 --> 38:45.044
I didn't get to say this before,

38:45.046 --> 38:46.814
so I need to say it now.

38:48.783 --> 38:51.250
You are who I should have wanted.

38:51.252 --> 38:53.218
You were right.

38:53.220 --> 38:56.288
<i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

38:56.290 --> 38:59.325
HAYLEY: <i>But I could never
manage to give up Elijah.</i>

38:59.327 --> 39:01.828
<i>I couldn't walk away.</i>

39:01.830 --> 39:05.998
FREYA: <i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

39:06.000 --> 39:10.770
I met him at a time in my
life when I was scared, alone.

39:10.772 --> 39:12.741
I know that's messed up.

39:14.743 --> 39:17.810
I guess I never really...

39:17.812 --> 39:21.381
saw what love was supposed to look like.

39:21.383 --> 39:25.183
<i>Verha hel igjen. Verha hel igjen.</i>

39:25.185 --> 39:27.319
<i>Verha hel igjen.</i>

39:27.321 --> 39:30.189
<i>Verha hel igjen.</i>

39:30.191 --> 39:33.091
♪ You will always be
every one of these... ♪

39:33.093 --> 39:35.861
But I don't want that for Hope.

39:35.863 --> 39:37.832
I wish she knew you.

39:39.868 --> 39:42.100
I wish a lot of things.

39:42.102 --> 39:44.437
<i>As for Elijah,</i>

39:44.439 --> 39:47.439
<i>I know what he is.</i>

39:47.441 --> 39:49.741
<i>I guess I always knew.</i>

39:49.744 --> 39:53.630
<i>But I loved him despite
it, or maybe because of it.</i>

39:53.633 --> 39:55.301
FREYA: <i>Verha hel igjen.</i>

39:56.718 --> 39:59.951
♪ Nothing's fair in love and war... ♪

39:59.953 --> 40:04.290
Truth is, I'm a monster, too.

40:04.292 --> 40:06.859
We've all done terrible things, Jack.

40:06.861 --> 40:08.895
Except for Hope.

40:08.897 --> 40:12.464
She's innocent, pure.

40:12.466 --> 40:15.147
And I want to make
sure she stays that way.

40:15.150 --> 40:18.770
♪ In love and war. ♪

40:18.772 --> 40:22.207
I know what I have to do.

40:22.209 --> 40:25.444
I just have to be brave enough to do it.

40:25.446 --> 40:27.415
♪ ♪

40:33.321 --> 40:35.821
I saw the light under your door.

40:35.823 --> 40:38.079
Your mother told me she tucked you in.

40:38.082 --> 40:40.618
I don't like to sleep
when things are happening.

40:41.830 --> 40:43.261
You woke Elijah.

40:43.263 --> 40:46.899
Yes. And he's very excited to see you.

40:46.901 --> 40:50.272
In the morning, hmm?

40:53.040 --> 40:56.075
There's nothing to worry
about anymore, okay?

40:56.077 --> 40:58.111
You didn't punish Kol.

40:58.113 --> 41:00.946
Well...

41:00.948 --> 41:02.448
he's family.

41:02.450 --> 41:04.350
And we protect family.

41:04.352 --> 41:07.120
Like you and mom are
my protectors, right?

41:07.122 --> 41:10.422
Always and forever.

41:10.424 --> 41:13.763
Tomorrow, I'm going to show you

41:13.766 --> 41:16.129
everything I love about New Orleans.

41:16.131 --> 41:19.098
The music, the dancing,

41:19.100 --> 41:20.500
the art.

41:20.502 --> 41:25.974
After all, every princess
ought to know her kingdom.

41:28.776 --> 41:30.745
Good night, sweetheart.

41:32.147 --> 41:33.716
Good night.

